{
  "texts": [
    "It therefore reduced the stereotype of the use of AI/GenAI applications being reserved to high-skilled programmers, engineers, or developers.",
    "Only during its first release year, ChatGPT reached more than 100 million customers around the world [42].",
    "The current version of GPT, GPT4, is more advanced than its predecessors with several useful additions such as a larger pre-trained dataset (trained on data up to December 2023 versus September 2021 for GPT3.5), more accuracy, larger context window, and much more presented by Ope-nAI [43].",
    "One of the most notable additions is its ability to respond to input images and even audio, making it even more user-friendly.",
    "OpenAI promises the addition of video recognition in future versions of GPT models.Inspired by some of GPT4's advanced technical additions, we integrated it as the LLM backbone of our system."
  ]
}